elements.description: Party invitations welcome sequins as well as subtlety and our collection runs the gamut between both. From ruffled, one-shoulder and puff-sleeve dresses to minimal tops, skirts and trousers, the edit caters to every occasion. Complement eveningwear with our collection of accessories including clutch bags and scarves, while for daytime parties, our collection of shimmering jewellery and headwear will raise the bar. Complete your party look with a colour-pop lipstick from our beauty collection and a pair of statement flat or heeled shoes.
